         <div type="notes">
            <note xml:id="n02120401" n="1">North and South 
        <name type="place" key="North Gabourie Creek">Gabourie</name>creeks run just above and
        below 
        <name type="place" key="Sainte Genevieve, Mo.">Ste. Genevieve</name>. The name is perhaps
        taken from 
        <name type="person" key="Gabourie, Laurent">Laurent Gabourie</name>, an early French
        settler. Houck, 1:339.</note>
            <note xml:id="n02120402" n="2">Perhaps 
        <name type="place" key="Turkey Island">Turkey Island</name>and 
        <name type="place" key="Prairie du Rocher Creek">Prairie du Rocher Creek</name>, in 
