        <name type="place" key="Illinois">Illinois</name>.</note>
            <note xml:id="n02120403" n="3">Perhaps what is shown as 
        <name type="place" key="Gray's Cave">Gray's Cave</name>on Raynolds &amp; Simpson, map
        5.</note>
            <note xml:id="n02120404" n="4">This may be 
        <name type="place" key="Frenchman Creek">Frenchman Creek</name>.</note>
            <note xml:id="n02120405" n="5">This camp was in 
        <name type="place" key="Jefferson County, Mo.">Jefferson County</name>, 
        <name type="place" key="Missouri">Missouri</name>. The island may be 
